&lt;p&gt;The structure of the content image could be easily extracted using the output of the last convolutional layer of vgg16.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Representation of Style&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
