&lt;h1&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VGG 16 was used to extract the feature and reconstruct images.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training the network takes very long time, a light CNN may be used for time reduction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The tune of parameter α and β to change the output.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
